The Local Key is retrieved from the Tuya IoT Platform. Follow our setup guide for API access.

[Setup Guide](https://github.com/moag1000/HA-kkt-kolbe-integration#-tuya-api-setup---vollstaendige-anleitung) | [Tuya IoT Platform](https://iot.tuya.com)

